reviews.review_text: ex show pg-vg rec Wonderful show. Recording is quite good too. Set 2 seems a bit lesser in sonic quality especially toward the end. But still an excellent listen.

Great "Playin"! Overall, a solid show, but the version of "Playin'" on this one gets the blue ribbon. About as jazzy as it gets for '81 (Kreutzmann summons '73-'74 mid-way through this monster jam). The rest of the show plain kicks ass. Lots of positive character to this AUD.
